I) Install subliminal:

1) Download the repo from https://github.com/Diaoul/subliminal

2) change install_requirements from gitRepository/setup.py with:

install_requirements = ['guessit==0.9.1', 'babelfish>=0.5.2', 'enzyme>=0.4.1', 'beautifulsoup4>=4.2.0',
'requests>=2.0', 'click==4.0', 'dogpile.cache>=0.5.4', 'stevedore>=1.0.0',
'chardet>=2.3.0', 'pysrt>=1.0.1', 'six>=1.9.0']

3) Open terminal and run: 
cd folder/to/repo
sudo python setup.py install
subliminal #this should show the help for subliminal

If above steps fail, open the terminal and:
ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)" < /dev/null 2> /dev/null
brew install subliminal


II) Download VLC 3.0 from http://nightlies.videolan.org/
download: Mac OS X Intel -> last

Update settings: "Interface-->Main Interfaces-->QT-->Continue playback?"


III) Copy download_subs.py to your home folder (in ~)


IV) How to use it:

cd ~
python download_subs.py /path/to/movies